We add a file `RingTheory.Trace.Quotient` gathering results about the relations between the trace map on `B → A` and the trace map on quotients and localizations.

Co-authored-by: Andrew Yang <36414270+erdOne@users.noreply.github.com>

OK, that makes sense. Anyway we should probably split `IntegrallyClosed` into `defs` `basic` etc. (I will do in another PR.)
